I7sX5qyTl9r5N8LiQkvxvwtCnXC0zb-04ySb2TnCFyk5ryv1DtfUQ2A3DudMYtd5MjXWbaICu5"], "content": "<div class=\"post-body entry-content\" id=\"post-body-3702407246193547703\" itemprop=\"description articleBody\">\n <p>\n </p>\n <div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\">\n  <br/>\n </div>\n <b>\n  Nova concentra\u00e7\u00e3o de massa,\n </b>\n An\u00e1logo ao anterior, ocorreu hoje em frente ao port\u00e3o central do Certh Research Center, em Thessaloniki. O centro, que absorve grandes fundos e \u00e9 considerado um \"centro tecnol\u00f3gico\" (com visitas do primeiro -ministro), demitiu recentemente cerca de 15 trabalhadores (sob o pretexto de \"Projeto N\u00e3o Individador\"). De fato, alguns s\u00e3o claramente vingativos, pois os trabalhadores redundantes eram trabalhadores sindicais.\n <p>\n </p>\n <div>\n  <div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\">\n   <img alt=\"\" data-original-height=\"722\" data-original-width=\"1600\" height=\"144\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/a/AVvXsEjH9FVzmDGW1o_AQMZDuTvEKs3zSltlnJFgcBNyLLoGeYT5wqHSSmZv5fMEjaGq5KNanwm6uYOnr44G0LS4Wzbk-AsLG7Tyci-02NgrpY6a2SfGx5U5uciesR5VOly6Q9jgc8JTNKLTQxOjTE2mu74t9o8pkOJfj4rLUgZEKGCKBqOjO7Zt5uIpagBTcEb3\" srcset=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/a/AVvXsEjH9FVzmDGW1o_AQMZDuTvEKs3zSltlnJFgcBNyLLoGeYT5wqHSSmZv5fMEjaGq5KNanwm6uYOnr44G0LS4Wzbk-AsLG7Tyci-02NgrpY6a2SfGx5U5uciesR5VOly6Q9jgc8JTNKLTQxOjTE2mu74t9o8pkOJfj4rLUgZEKGCKBqOjO7Zt5uIpagBTcEb3\" width=\"320\"/>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\">\n   <br/>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\">\n   <div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\">\n    <img alt=\"\" data-original-height=\"722\" data-original-width=\"1600\" height=\"144\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/a/AVvXsEh9BwOOIJ4ByX7Cig21VFwi5fImwCkauSz5lY0DguGrfwphc3BRLdn9Cu1-KEiwzzUVNNk-69SxjDWfl-fLDmjqpfut4Ldu3Xho40i4Kt4_yQPqAGVWzr8nK9sIhB_J6JKHninGoeS9MjdvoxJlaixxqe7ndSJLsBlJcPKufv-t2r7mz6umN2AMlkpactZ_\" srcset=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/a/AVvXsEh9BwOOIJ4ByX7Cig21VFwi5fImwCkauSz5lY0DguGrfwphc3BRLdn9Cu1-KEiwzzUVNNk-69SxjDWfl-fLDmjqpfut4Ldu3Xho40i4Kt4_yQPqAGVWzr8nK9sIhB_J6JKHninGoeS9MjdvoxJlaixxqe7ndSJLsBlJcPKufv-t2r7mz6umN2AMlkpactZ_\" width=\"320\"/>\n   </div>\n   <span>\n    <a name=\"more\">\n    </a>\n   </span>\n   <div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\">\n    <br/>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: left;\">\n    <p>\n     <b>\n      A grande maioria dos trabalhadores do centro est\u00e1 trabalhando com a DPY. (\"Bloquear\")\n     </b>\n     , com o que isso implica: contratos de curto prazo, n\u00e3o permiss\u00f5es (normais, doentes e parentes), n\u00e3o horas fixas e horas extras pagas, sem compensa\u00e7\u00e3o de demiss\u00e3o. Com base no \"bloco\", a administra\u00e7\u00e3o do centro se disfar\u00e7a com o t\u00edtulo enganoso \"Contrato de Finaliza\u00e7\u00e3o\". A necessidade de reivindicar um trabalho permanente e est\u00e1vel, mais do que \u00f3bvio.\n    </p>\n    <p>\n    </p>\n    <p>\n     <b>\n      Nesta base,\n     </b>\n     E ap\u00f3s a primeira mobiliza\u00e7\u00e3o, os sindicatos Setip, SMT-M e voc\u00ea foi convidado para uma reuni\u00e3o conjunta realizada no Ekth, com uma participa\u00e7\u00e3o significativa, e decidiu ter um novo com\u00edcio. Uma impress\u00e3o alien\u00edgena causou a atitude da \"Associa\u00e7\u00e3o dos Trabalhadores\", que se comportou como um empregador genu\u00edno. Mais ou menos abalou o dedo para os trabalhadores e se recusou a chamar a mobiliza\u00e7\u00e3o! N\u00e3o \u00e9 por acaso, ent\u00e3o, que o governo encaminhou os 3 sindicatos a ... SeeketA (!) Para o desempenho de suas resolu\u00e7\u00f5es. Os funcion\u00e1rios t\u00eam olhos e veem quem est\u00e1 do seu lado e quem com o empregador ...\n    </p>\n    <p>\n    </p>\n    <div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\">\n     <img alt=\"\" data-original-height=\"722\" data-original-width=\"1600\" height=\"144\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/a/AVvXsEiiD_ROfczryb1ej8l63gPmS8bgyCThFY0N-gl9DgSPyIuLCtX_zH7VTRZA79dwJkemjOtOvPwrdBi9UwVUFXCdCvUNNTgZ0op9Pz3ZdXEvAun44IoSnKTAeN8E9M2IjffWTpJRxxI4crU3-8jsytAjm1WOxHw_L41pjkrkczhIpubcmtYUcvuA_l5GVqsC\" srcset=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/a/AVvXsEiiD_ROfczryb1ej8l63gPmS8bgyCThFY0N-gl9DgSPyIuLCtX_zH7VTRZA79dwJkemjOtOvPwrdBi9UwVUFXCdCvUNNTgZ0op9Pz3ZdXEvAun44IoSnKTAeN8E9M2IjffWTpJRxxI4crU3-8jsytAjm1WOxHw_L41pjkrkczhIpubcmtYUcvuA_l5GVqsC\" width=\"320\"/>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\">\n     <br/>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\">\n     <div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\">\n      <img alt=\"\" data-original-height=\"722\" data-original-width=\"1600\" height=\"144\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/a/AVvXsEjwzip6huSLuiz28T89o92NvCFbzrF52VYfIC2DVTdxqlBLJVaO2DZrzkSDVZhbux6vNPmVbN63NwNALN0aR3oX2avlKlx4tNWGJXexd4236flI7d_x-x-MkNXkodoAhArNn1qe_5rxBYjzJy_Isawa0u-gf-g9RTPDWtVg7EoK_sAT6IbVLtigcd_j6gzG\" srcset=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/a/AVvXsEjwzip6huSLuiz28T89o92NvCFbzrF52VYfIC2DVTdxqlBLJVaO2DZrzkSDVZhbux6vNPmVbN63NwNALN0aR3oX2avlKlx4tNWGJXexd4236flI7d_x-x-MkNXkodoAhArNn1qe_5rxBYjzJy_Isawa0u-gf-g9RTPDWtVg7EoK_sAT6IbVLtigcd_j6gzG\" width=\"320\"/>\n     </div>\n     <div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\">\n      <br/>\n     </div>\n     <div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: left;\">\n      <div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\">\n       <img alt=\"\" data-original-height=\"722\" data-original-width=\"1600\" height=\"144\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/a/AVvXsEi9kwHxmBb39YeCNfK0l0-Fs5MrTG26Yp612zoUFslNz9tEofzB6-jFFxoPvL6u919RqFn3nSPRYAARFF94rfdhSrnQF-PmF61cE8hw2own_BCOEUTLzocWX5XD_11BD3bpC7r6Vt5UdW2p_6m6b_QfR_Au0yLOEgu5B9jvx8LrZhh_IX-EV7e8CtH6uXcQ\" srcset=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/a/AVvXsEi9kwHxmBb39YeCNfK0l0-Fs5MrTG26Yp612zoUFslNz9tEofzB6-jFFxoPvL6u919RqFn3nSPRYAARFF94rfdhSrnQF-PmF61cE8hw2own_BCOEUTLzocWX5XD_11BD3bpC7r6Vt5UdW2p_6m6b_QfR_Au0yLOEgu5B9jvx8LrZhh_IX-EV7e8CtH6uXcQ\" width=\"320\"/>\n      </div>\n      <br/>\n      <br/>\n     </div>\n     <div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\">\n      <img alt=\"\" data-original-height=\"722\" data-original-width=\"1600\" height=\"144\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/a/AVvXsEihP_ZGp8qMmeicrgzXPLOG52EMLSL-YfZZn-D-cP5DI90f-vc6pmfIqFl5dDYafk12w24KrZ7JoI7TIXJmhqS8Dh5lL1cjxLzBSPd56CqwQ6zMTciHc07KHRlnKigYAOQU7eUTJzynLuHM7LYszgQnb2A_GUxyVamgbrElTqqWy4ihkLjz1319hD1UEIEb\" srcset=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/a/AVvXsEihP_ZGp8qMmeicrgzXPLOG52EMLSL-YfZZn-D-cP5DI90f-vc6pmfIqFl5dDYafk12w24KrZ7JoI7TIXJmhqS8Dh5lL1cjxLzBSPd56CqwQ6zMTciHc07KHRlnKigYAOQU7eUTJzynLuHM7LYszgQnb2A_GUxyVamgbrElTqqWy4ihkLjz1319hD1UEIEb\" width=\"320\"/>\n     </div>\n     <br/>\n     <div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\">\n      <img alt=\"\" data-original-height=\"722\" data-original-width=\"1600\" height=\"144\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/a/AVvXsEjqgtB3FoYHC84VrHxhvqr44wiible9lDBSrW1AuSGLZvJ5RdnClA58xh5feVEvNY8nqDXQJLJmtGj2qb9Vy5lInBP6-MKKz4L6bWN2HZDC5Ihxik0RHZfx_NZPFiH-lsebtIlSfifa6O95AK7jNmaMPA0ETA-pPRQdEDtoD78H8oBkTlrJBqd1ETLxo46f\" srcset=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/a/AVvXsEjqgtB3FoYHC84VrHxhvqr44wiible9lDBSrW1AuSGLZvJ5RdnClA58xh5feVEvNY8nqDXQJLJmtGj2qb9Vy5lInBP6-MKKz4L6bWN2HZDC5Ihxik0RHZfx_NZPFiH-lsebtIlSfifa6O95AK7jNmaMPA0ETA-pPRQdEDtoD78H8oBkTlrJBqd1ETLxo46f\" width=\"320\"/>\n     </div>\n     <br/>\n    </div>\n    <p>\n    </p>\n    <p>\n     <b>\n      A concentra\u00e7\u00e3o de hoje \u00e9 julgada bem -sucedida\n     </b>\n     , como em termos de massa, levantou a quest\u00e3o de redund\u00e2ncias e rela\u00e7\u00f5es de trabalho. Esses com\u00edcios d\u00e3o coragem e solidariedade pr\u00e1tica aos trabalhadores no local de trabalho e, \u00e9 claro, enviam uma mensagem e empurram o empregador. O fato de essas mobiliza\u00e7\u00f5es serem levadas a s\u00e9rio pela presen\u00e7a de uma gaiola de tapete em frente ao port\u00e3o, o que \u00e9 provavelmente o \u00fanico \"argumento\" que o governo pode propor contra os direitos ...\n    </p>\n    <div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\">\n     <div style=\"text-align: left;\">\n      <p>\n      </p>\n      <p>\n       <b>\n        Na reuni\u00e3o que eles participaram\n       </b>\n       : Setip, SMT-M, Seee, associa\u00e7\u00f5es de estudantes, sindicatos \u00e0 esquerda e anarquista. A iniciativa de corrida e a marcha da classe tiveram uma presen\u00e7a significativa na manifesta\u00e7\u00e3o, bem como um papel na organiza\u00e7\u00e3o de todas as etapas da evolu\u00e7\u00e3o.\n      </p>\n      <p>\n      </p>\n      <div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\">\n       <img alt=\"\" data-original-height=\"1205\" data-original-width=\"1600\" height=\"240\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/a/AVvXsEhQIX8VtZVmLT3vo1KasL3BtpAs0rzmI78bk0WMwpaqewtVWpBkuqNbYJ5gN1W0aJkUUbg1RaSvBqZRyaOHeL3uwjbPZdza_oGDjacGflypt7XksIX_KMI7sX5qyTl9r5N8LiQkvxvwtCnXC0zb-04ySb2TnCFyk5ryv1DtfUQ2A3DudMYtd5MjXWbaICu5\" srcset=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/a/AVvXsEhQIX8VtZVmLT3vo1KasL3BtpAs0rzmI78bk0WMwpaqewtVWpBkuqNbYJ5gN1W0aJkUUbg1RaSvBqZRyaOHeL3uwjbPZdza_oGDjacGflypt7XksIX_KMI7sX5qyTl9r5N8LiQkvxvwtCnXC0zb-04ySb2TnCFyk5ryv1DtfUQ2A3DudMYtd5MjXWbaICu5\" width=\"319\"/>\n      </div>\n      <br/>\n      <br/>\n      <p>\n      </p>\n     </div>\n     <br/>\n    </div>\n    <p>\n     <br/>\n     <br/>\n    </p>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <br/>\n  <br/>\n </div>\n <div style=\"clear: both;\">\n </div>\n</div>\n", "description": "", "author": ["\u03a3.\u039c."], "labels": ["\u03b1\u03c0\u03bf\u03bb\u03c5\u03c3\u03b5\u03b9\u03c2", "\u03b5\u03c1\u03b3\u03b1\u03b6\u03bf\u03bc\u03b5\u03bd\u03bf\u03b9", "\u03b8\u03b5\u03c3\u03c3\u03b1\u03bb\u03bf\u03bd\u03b9\u03ba\u03b7", "\u039a\u03b9\u03bd\u03b7\u03c4\u03bf\u03c0\u03bf\u03af\u03b7\u03c3\u03b7"], "source": "https://antigeitonies3.blogspot.com/2024/02/blog-post_31.html"}